episodes.title: The Yellow Deli Cult | The REAL Story
episodes.description: The Yellow Deli - sounds innocents enough, right? It’s a restaurant chain that prides itself on wholesome homemade food, like hot steam sandwiches, fresh salads and desserts like sweet potato pound cake. The Real Story about The Yellow Deli will turn your stomach. It starts with a sandwich… but ends with mind control, child labor, and the loss of personal freedom. You think you’re walking into a cozy café—but you’re actually walking into a cult.
